Basically, Factory method is a method that is defined in Parent class and is implemented in Child class, which usually is abstract method.
By contract, Template method is a method that implements an &ldquo;algorithm&rdquo;. This implementation is usually defined in a &ldquo;Parent&rdquo; class and leveraging other methods including Factory methods. (See sample below)
